{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/belaboom.gif?t=1734554864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tower Defense meets Idle Clicker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a Tower Defense x Idle Clicker game set inside the Crayon Empire. Let the game build out your bases, upgrade your colorful forces and attack all oncoming enemy forces. Or take charge and control your destiny and fortify your defenses. As the game levels up and enemies get stronger, you will be rewarded new weapon choices and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/ss001-idle-special.gif?t=1734554864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Idle Special</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you let the game idle in the background, the &quot;Idle Special&quot; bar will slowly fill up. When it is fully ready, click that button! It will unleash a powerful attack on all the unsuspecting enemies trying to harm your base. Impatient and can't wait for it to fill up? Click click click and fill it in faster! Might unleash even powerful attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/moonbase.gif?t=1734554864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Auto Defenses Deployed</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Got something else to take care of? Step away and let the game handle your defenses for you! Your base, your tower defenses and game level itself will slowly level up and upgrade over time allowing for more weapon types, abilities and more to be used to defend against the evil space empire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/karabelt.gif?t=1734554864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 20 different custom Maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 different Game Modes: Idle and Death</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music Player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cloud Saves</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734554864","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/page.bg.jpg?t=1734554864","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/903df377bb58ca1f7cac2037e436062c6d1e6796/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734554864","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/903df377bb58ca1f7cac2037e436062c6d1e6796/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734554864","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/belaboom.gif?t=1734554864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tower Defense meets Idle Clicker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a Tower Defense x Idle Clicker game set inside the Crayon Empire. Let the game build out your bases, upgrade your colorful forces and attack all oncoming enemy forces. Or take charge and control your destiny and fortify your defenses. As the game levels up and enemies get stronger, you will be rewarded new weapon choices and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_par